    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of small tree native to the dry savanna woodlands of Africa and western India; valued as timber since ancient Egyptian times. Not a true ebony.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
